{"tags":[{"name":"工具","permalink":"http://catlittlechen.com/tags/工具/","url":"/async/tags/工具.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"学习","permalink":"http://catlittlechen.com/categories/学习/","url":"/async/categories/学习.json","count":8}],"url":"/async/posts/2018/08/13/tmux.json","date":1534139823000,"path":{"year":2018,"month":8,"day":13,"name":"tmux"},"title":"tmux","permalink":"http://catlittlechen.com/2018/08/13/tmux/","content":"<h2 id=\"tmux\"><a href=\"#tmux\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"tmux\"></a>tmux</h2><p>新的公司，开发需要远程到另外一台开发机器上，所以开始使用 tmux，虽然还是喜欢 ubuntu 的 terminal 多一些点。</p>\n<h3 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"install\"></a>install</h3><figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/tmux/tmux.git /tmp/tmux</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /tmp/tmux</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git checkout 2.8</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ sh autogen.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ ./configure &amp;&amp; make</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"conf\"><a href=\"#conf\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"conf\"></a>conf</h3><figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/gpakosz/.tmux.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ ln -s -f .tmux/.tmux.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cp .tmux/.tmux.conf.local .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Bindings\"><a href=\"#Bindings\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Bindings\"></a>Bindings</h3><ul>\n<li><p><code>&lt;prefix&gt;</code> 等价于 <code>ctrl + b</code> 或者 <code>ctrl + a</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>切屏</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; -</code> 水平切分 –&gt; tmux split</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; _</code> 垂直切分 –&gt; tmux split -h</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>切换</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; hjkl</code> 切换分部</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; HJKL</code> 分部大小整理</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; +</code> 将当前屏幕切分到另外一个窗口</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>窗口</p>\n<ul>\n<li>tmux new-window</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; ctrl h</code> 切换前一个窗口</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; ctrl l</code> 切换后一个窗口</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; number</code> 切换指定窗口</li>\n<li><code>&lt;prefix&gt; w</code> 可以选择窗口哦</li>\n<li>tmux rename-window $newName</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"#Usage\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Usage\"></a>Usage</h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\">tmux new -s work</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"keyword\">do</span> something</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\">&lt;prefix&gt; d</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\">tmux a -s work</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>"}